contentrichtext.text: '''Dnieper''', '''Dnepr''' (Russian), or '''Dnipro''' (Ukrainian) can mean: * [[Dnieper River]] * [[Dnieper Ukraine]], central Ukraine under the Russian Empire * [[Dnepr rocket]], a space rocket. * [[Dnipro (Kiev Metro)]], a Metro station in Kiev * [[Dnepr (motorcycle)]] * [[FC Dnepr Smolensk]], a Russian football club * [[FC Dnipro Dnipropetrovsk]], a football club from Ukraine * [[FC Dnepr Mahilyow]], a football club from Belarus * Dnepr was the call sign of the Soviet [[Soyuz T-7]] mission to space station Salyut 7. * [[Ukrainian Dnipro Ensemble of Edmonton]] {{Disambig}}
